{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act37side", "eventName": "追跡日落以西", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GO-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "酒精與安慰劑", "storyInfo": "戰時，並肩作戰的士兵們歌唱著走向勝利的未來，但如今的一切卻並未完全如他們所願。而維娜也同樣並不完全滿意自己當下為這座城市所爭取來的一切。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g1_battlefieldoutside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.5, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……少尉……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希勒……少尉……快……起來……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看到了一雙手伸向了自己。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴……戴菲恩小姐？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "walk1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walk1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動，我背著你，我們得趕快撤回我們攻下來的安全駐地。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能還會有更多薩卡茲部隊來搜查或用巫術炸彈攔截我們。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——謝謝您——救了我——", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必謝我，救你的是一位英勇的士兵，也是一位盡責的護理師——莎拉女士。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她強行催動還不熟練的源石技藝，擋下了巫術炸彈的爆炸，保護了那些還在轉運的傷員們，當然，也包括你。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是她……等等，難道她——", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，她只是昏過去了。我們已經把她帶回接駁口的臨時駐地。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你們都暴露在極高濃度的源石粉塵環境中太久……", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很清楚風險。", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩小姐，所以……你們成功了？抵達接駁口了？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到城牆上的火……熄滅了。", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城牆之戰……已經結束了？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這場仗才剛開始。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食腐者仰仗著城防炮以及最精銳的部隊與公爵聯軍僵持不下。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們……能做點什麼嗎？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突破接駁口，為聯軍開出一道缺口，逼薩卡茲露出破綻。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像聯軍“幫”我們一樣……儘管這並非他們的本意。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了——咳咳——", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希勒少尉，接下來的任務你不用參加。這是命令。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是推進之王的命令——", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的命令。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉，留在接駁口的駐地，你現在需要的是休息。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attrib