d": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賜予我們無盡的恩典♪", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你怎麼不唱啊？", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "悲傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小子，別一副愁眉苦臉的樣子！大家不都帶著傷嗎？但我們已經快到家門口了！", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們歡樂地歌唱♪", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞，我的故鄉！♪", "name": "積極的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維、維多利亞……我的故鄉！♪", "name": "悲傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小子，我的口糧吃不完，分你一點吧。", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是我們回家後的第一頓早餐，當然得吃飽一點！", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我們的大部隊進了城，就讓那些魔族佬們見識一下誰才是倫蒂尼姆真正的主人！", "name": "積極的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "嘖，我不喜歡這首歌……"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "維娜，你說呢？"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別問她了，她自己有時候睡覺都還會哼這首歌呢。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜！", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因陀羅，你有這空閒不如多吃幾口飯。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者乾脆分給我，等一下突擊行動我來打頭陣。畢竟你在突進赦罪師密道的時候受了傷。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想得美，這點小傷根本沒差。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，我揍人時可不會被這種傷拖累。達格達，這次你別想搶在我前面！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我吃完了，我帶人再巡邏一圈確認周圍狀況，確保行動萬無一失。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然軍委會選擇布防在只有修築城牆工人們才知道的備用接駁口，代表他們對城內的掌控範圍可能遠超我們的預期。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩小姐，巡邏工作我已經完成了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，可以分我一些口糧嗎？我還沒吃早餐呢。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉？！你……你不是受傷還在休息嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，我是軍醫。我很清楚該怎麼最快讓一名士兵恢復戰鬥力。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩小姐，我很清楚自己的狀況。我現在正式歸隊，參與你們的行動。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉，你把防護設備讓給傷員，自己卻暴露在高濃度源石環境裡，還正面承受巫術炸彈的衝擊……那你應該很清楚自己的身體狀況。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然知道。雖然沒辦法做血液檢測，但我很清楚感染後會發生什麼事。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那又如何？在這裡，這算是什麼特別的事嗎？", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他環顧四周，典範軍的士兵們擠在不算寬敞的通道附近。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塵土與源石粉塵成了他們臉上最好的偽裝，但他們的眼神卻始終沒有一刻黯淡。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們很清楚自己在做什麼，也清楚將要付出什麼代價。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在，他們在歌唱。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歡樂地歌唱♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，戴菲恩，你同意少尉歸隊嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩看向希勒少尉的手，他試圖藏在身後的東西還是被她看到了——一支止痛劑。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在難以獲得足夠的礦石病抑制劑時，止痛劑是唯一能緩解疼痛的選擇。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你撐得住嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。戴菲恩小姐，別忘了，我還想親眼見證您回家，拿回本該屬於您的東西呢。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……本來可以不用參與的。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不也一樣嗎？", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然您想看到這支隊伍能走到何處，這座城市會變成什麼樣子，那我也一樣。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1070_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好，少尉，歸隊吧。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜老大，等我們把那些魔族佬全趕跑後，倫蒂尼姆會變成什麼樣子？", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肯定會比以前好吧。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就希望城裡多開幾家花店，這樣花的價格能便宜一點，我才好找位有錢的小姐或剛喪夫的夫人結婚。", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望源石燃料能多一點，爐子燒得更旺，冬天別再這麼冷。", "name": "積極的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_423_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_241", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我希望能有更多的好警察局，自己能當個好警察，最好真的能幫到別人，而不是只會剝削別人的血汗錢。", "name": "冷靜的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小子，你呢？", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我只希望回家的時候，媽媽還會在門口等著我。", "name": "悲傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，當然會的！等我們回家了，你媽媽一定會在門口迎接你！", "name": "開朗的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達，你呢？要繼續跟我們一起重建拳館，還是躲回你的塔樓裡？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜，我還沒跟你打夠呢。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#12$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，到時候，我們一起回拳館！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然……我們會回家的……但我們還沒找到貝爾德呢……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#2$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>跨進家門的這一步，我們足足走了三天。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>而迎接我們的，是工廠噴出的漫天蒸汽。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>但……更多的人卻倒在了家門前。他們唱著歌，走進通道的深處，卻再也沒有回來。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g5_victoriaspeakeasy", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>“一鎊十杯”酒館</><p=2>1098年12月21日 5:25 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_248", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜老大，這杯我請你！", "name": "興奮的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們雖然把魔族佬趕出去了，但他們可沒死光！他們手上還有能讓整座城市飄滿源石塵的技術，肯定還會再打回來！", "name": "興奮的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那些公爵，要是哪天又出了什麼事，他們還是不會管我們死活！", "name": "魯莽的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是你說的，我們得有保護自己的力量。", "name": "魯莽的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以啊，我根本不信外面那些傳言——“解散典範軍”，你說對吧，維娜老大？", "name": "魯莽的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還記得那天我們在接駁口說過的願望嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望工廠的爐火能像以前一樣旺盛，城牆上的城防炮能像過去一樣守護倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有希望每個區的警察局都能敞開大門，警察不再對貴族唯命是從，也不會無端驅趕感染者……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望唯一的規則是議會通過的法律……這一直是我的目標，我也在努力實現它。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們滿意現在的倫蒂尼姆嗎？它變得更好了嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "魯莽的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_248", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "興奮的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，說實話我並不滿意。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在避重就輕，議長閣下，他們並他們不是在質問你。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你什麼都不做，讓典範軍維持現狀，至少現在大家還能接受。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們只想要一個確切的答案——典範軍還能繼續存在嗎？", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉，這就是我的回答。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議會擔心你們對我的信任已經超過了對議會的信任。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許他們害怕的是典範軍終究會變成維娜·維多利亞的私軍。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我害怕的是，到了那時典範軍還能維持它的榮耀嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當初許下的願望真的能有實現的一天嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝你們，我會將今天瞭解到的情況轉告議會。畢竟我也沒有資格擅自做決定。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，我們走吧。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你先走吧。我想留下來陪大家喝幾杯。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "sw"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5, "channel": "sw"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>那天，我沒能完全理解維娜的意思。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 240.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>但我贊同少尉的看法——典範軍的戰友需要我們的幫助……所以我留下來了，替維娜留下，至少陪他們聊聊天。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>明明她已經是議長了，明明她能做的事情比誰都多……</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>戰爭結束後的第一次，我喝得爛醉，那裡的烈酒嗆得我胃痛。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>最後是漢娜找到我。我終於鼓起勇氣問了她一個一直不敢問維娜的問題——</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>“我們什麼時候才能回家？回到我們的拳館？”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g7_towngreenhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藥草長得很好，黛安看到一定會很高興。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初農場重建時，多虧她說服工程隊把那些損壞的光照設備留下來，改裝成功率較低的小型溫室。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊，抱歉，剛剛我們聊到哪裡了？", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您最近的身體狀況。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您剛才提到自己的源石技藝出現了跨越式強化的跡象。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，抱歉，我的記性越來越差了，總是恍神，醫生說源石已經蔓延到腦裡了……", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我是不是已經跟你講過好幾次了？", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別在意，我們只是聊聊天，您想說什麼都可以。最近還有其他不尋常的地方嗎？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走路變得很難走直線？不過這應該不算什麼，很多人都有這種狀況吧。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共濟失調……倫蒂尼姆的很多感染者都有類似的症狀，但目前我對此沒什麼頭緒。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有啊，最近趁著獨處時我總會忍不住偷偷嘗試……真奇怪，我的源石技藝好像變了。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變了？之前的報告裡沒提到——", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，莎拉女士，請您繼續說。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，您是徒手施法的嗎？我想醫生應該提醒過您，這樣做會讓病情更難控制。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，您就跟黛安說的一樣，真是個愛操心的採訪者。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我總是想用這種方式，在自己愈發混沌的腦海裡找回那場戰役的記憶。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說城牆之戰。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您曾提到當時您還是名護理師，試圖用源石技藝抵擋巫術炸彈的爆炸，但……效果並不理想。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。我只記得那時我緊跟在希勒少尉身後，結果被巨大的衝擊力拋飛了出去。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我醒來時已經躺在臨時醫院，然後得知我和身邊的人都成了急性感染者。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會變成這樣呢，埃利西奧先生……我甚至不知道到底有多少顆巫術炸彈落在了典範軍之中。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼多人的命運在一瞬間被徹底改寫……可是我卻什麼都沒看清，什麼也回想不起來……", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_originiumcastshort", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……莎拉女士？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧察覺到患者的身體開始劇烈顫抖，甚至無意識地施放出源石技藝。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不確定這是否是創傷的後遺症之一，但幾乎是本能地，他立刻試圖引導對方。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——莎拉女士，請聽我說，跟著我深呼吸。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能聞到花香，對吧？你的身體還在這裡，這裡是一家療養院。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭已經結束了，典範軍也已經回家了。你已經回到了倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他話語一頓，下意識地抬頭望向頭頂那盞破損的光照設備。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市在他眼中早已滿目瘡痍，成為一座陌生城市。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你在一個……一切都會變得更好的地方。”"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g6_dusklentiavenue", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莎拉女士的源石技藝發生異變，這是以往從未在感染者身上觀察到的情況……我得請其他同事多加留意。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#9$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……不曉得黛安小姐能不能幫我聯絡國際信使？如果等梅蘭德的固定信使來取信，恐怕太遲了。我得儘快為倫蒂尼姆爭取物資……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step1", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，埃利西奧先生？你也在這？！", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你怎麼不攔住她？你不是一直在找她本人嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#9$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰……？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議長閣下。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——議長？！我剛剛才看到她從地下酒館出來……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是從那裡出來的。剛好遇上她去找以前的老朋友們喝酒。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……看來她真的把自己當成你們的朋友。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……要是不只是朋友就好了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生……我一直相信倫蒂尼姆會變得更好，讓維多利亞能為她感到驕傲。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，議長真的能做到這一切嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}